From: dfattal <dfattal@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:52:46 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 18/21] inline-3d(#625): XR_EXT_ -> XR_DXR_ extension rename
 (runtime v2.0.0)

Applied displayxr-runtime scripts/dxr_rename.py (allowlist-driven, exact
symbols + extension-name prefixes + struct-type block 1000999->1004999)
to components/displayxr + third_party/displayxr, then replaced the 12
vendored DisplayXR extension headers with byte-identical copies of the
runtime's canonical v2.0.0 set (Apache-2.0 + provisional-registration
notice + SPEC_VERSION restart). Verified live against installed runtime
v2.0.0: all extensions negotiate, xrWeaveBindWindowDXR -> 0, DP weaves.
Khronos XR_EXT_/XR_KHR_ names untouched. displayxr-browser#9
